Package: npiv
Type: Package
Title: Nonparametric Instrumental Variables Estimation and Inference
Version: 0.10-03
Date: 2024-12-10
Imports: progress, MASS, Formula
Author:  Jeffrey S. Racine, Timothy Christensen
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Jeffrey S.", family = "Racine", role = c("aut","cre"), email = "racinej@mcmaster.ca"),
             person(given = "Timothy", family = "Christensen", role = c("aut"), email = "timothy.christensen@yale.edu"))
Maintainer:  Timothy Christensen <timothy.christensen@yaleedu> 
Description: This package provides tools for adptive estimation and inference for nonparametric structural functions using instrumental variables. The methods apply to nonparametric regression as a special case. 
